Privacy Policy — Bulk YouTube Transcript Downloader
Last updated: April 27, 2026

1. Information We Collect
This app does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. We do not require account registration or login.

2. YouTube Data
The app fetches publicly available transcript data from YouTube videos using YouTube's public APIs. No user account credentials are requested or stored. The app does not access your YouTube account, watch history, or subscriptions.

3. Downloaded Files
Transcripts and subtitle files (.txt / .srt) are saved locally on your device only. We do not upload, sync, or transmit any downloaded content to our servers or third parties.

4. Internet Access
An internet connection is required solely to fetch video metadata and transcripts from YouTube. No data about your usage is sent to us.

5. Third-Party Services
This app uses Google's YouTube Data API. Use of YouTube data is subject to Google's Privacy Policy and YouTube's Terms of Service.

6. Analytics & Advertising
This app does not use any analytics SDKs, crash reporting tools, or advertising networks.

7. Children's Privacy
This app is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.

8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy. Any changes will be reflected by the updated date at the top of this page.
